{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"667","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"史上最高溫！南極首次紀錄熱浪 新研究憂生態浩劫","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-04-01 16:13:26</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%8D%97%E6%A5%B5%E7%86%B1%E6%B5%AA.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 533px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>南極在今年<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>23</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>26</span>日遭遇超級熱浪襲擊。（歐新社）</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕全球暖化持續加劇，南極今年初爆發超級熱浪，創下該地區有史以來最高溫紀錄，科學家對此事件進行的研究報告近日出爐，專家憂心，這種前所未見的現象恐對生態系帶來嚴重影響。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>根據《<span lang='EN-US'>CNN</span>》報導，最新發表在《全球變化生物學》期刊（<span lang='EN-US'>Global Change Biology journal</span>）的研究報告指出，南極在今年<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>23</span>至<span lang='EN-US'>26</span>日遭超級熱浪襲擊，當地最低溫度攀升至<span lang='EN-US'>0</span>度以上，最高溫度則達到攝氏<span lang='EN-US'>7.5</span>度左右，創下當地有史以來最高溫紀錄。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>南極生態學家柏格斯通博士（<span lang='EN-US'>Dana Bergstrom</span>）表示，異常溫暖的夏天將對當地物種帶來負面影響，並對整個生態系統構成威脅。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>柏格斯通解釋，當地大多數生命均存活在小型無冰綠洲中，在夏天時很大程度地依賴著緩慢的融冰提供水分，但在熱浪襲擊下冰融化的速度太快，可能會形成洪水，傷害生物群落；而快速融冰的另一個缺點便是，若冰雪在季初融化完畢，整個生態系統都將在剩下的季節內面臨乾旱的困境。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3119781</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-04-06","clk_count":"228"}},"__N_SSG":true}